text:
Okay I had to work out the pattern:

The ODESZA set is 23 minutes long and loops, with the same synced visuals each time, every 1 hour there's a 1 minute break, each with a different tune and visual.
At 3:39:00 there's a Music Dance Experience scene from the show but the music doesn't change.
With each passing hour the video loop gets more and more broken up.
The final hour has a few missing tracks so that it can end with the 23 min set end as a new clip.of Mark turning off the lights and going up the lift ends the 8 hour work day.
